column5: Yeah I know he,s not doing the best,but like all those Leaf fans,you stick with him through the bad times and good.  The ghost trailer and the daddy.

very nice addition to the collection.  If he were only still around just think of the fun he would have with little kyle.  i miss him everytime i sit down or listen to a race.  without a doubt he will always be The Man !  jason
Kyle wouldnt be around,if HE was still here.  TY
